PushGPIndividual
public abstract class GAIndividual
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

An abstract GP individual class containing a fitness value. The fitness value represents an individual's error values, such that lower fitness values are better and such that a fitness value of 0 indicates a perfect solution.
